                    <span>I have never written a negative review of a book before - but I was so disappointed in the investment I made in this book, I felt compelled to let others know. 
<br />I got the impression that the author made a few minor changes to a book about running a restaurant, slapped on a new title and released it. I feel this book is far too expensive to be anything less than the source of specialized information it is advertised to be.</span>
                  
